These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Job: analyst, librarian, coach, dressmaker
1. Job:librarian is in an odd position##4
2. Job:dressmaker is between Job:analyst and Job:librarian##2
3. Job:dressmaker is on the right of Job:analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Job   | analyst | dressmaker | librarian | coach |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: comedy, scientific, animation, superhero
1. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Movie-Genre:scientific is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:comedy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | comedy | superhero | animation |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
