.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Color: grey, fuchsia, brown, pink
1. Color:fuchsia == Color:fuchsia##1
2. Color:pink is on the left or right of Color:brown##3
3. Color:brown is on the far left or far right##3
4. Color:grey is in an even position##4
5. Color:pink is on the left of Color:fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Color   | brown | pink | fuchsia | grey |

